	   <a name=101277664451090></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101277664451090><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=6&mid=101277664451090>Choices!</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=6&mid=101277664451090#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=119883><span id=Scholar>Burgen</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>58 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Feb 3rd 6:52 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.45]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello Brothers!<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;  I have yet another dilemma. I recently picked up a Mith Two Handed Sword from EC for 300pp.  I currently use a Worn Crescant Axe as my 2HS but was wondering which would be better to use in the long run.  The Axe has some really nice stats, +3 to STR, DEX, and AGI plus 10Hp.  <br>    Now, to add to the choice I had a high level player hand me an Argent Defender shorthly after acquiring the Mith Two Hander because he got tired of trying to sell it.  It too is a nice sword! Choices, choices!  Needless to say I don't need to be hoofing around three 2HS weapons and need to sell off one or two.  The question is which??  Your suggestions, as always, are most welcome.<br>     Be well, and be safe!<br>&nbsp;<br>Burgen Battleblood Paladin of the 59th Season<br>Realm Powers<br>Zebuxoruk Server</td></tr>
