	   <tr><td colspan=2>All of the spells you get are farely useful in one way or another.&nbsp;&nbsp;As for sense heading, asine those to your user defined slots and match them up with your direction keys.  Then everytime you hit a direction you'll practice sense heading.  <br><br>As for hunting, you're primarily kept to east commons and North Ro.  However, you could also head into unrest around level 10.  They have made that dungeon better suited to lower level players.  Keep a lantern in the bank though, because as a human paladin you won't be able to see to get your corpse back.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
