	   <tr><td colspan=2>Heh.. I just wanted to post for all begining paladins out there.&nbsp;&nbsp;You will be taunted and made to feel inferior to the other classes at times.  Do not listen to them!!!  I was oblivious to this at low levels as my pally was my first character.  However at level 39, trying to get a group in the dreadlands I shouted something like 39 PALADIN lfg.. and was met by shouts mocking our holy class.  I made it a goal at that point to duel every class at an equal level... this I have done..... and won.. every one.<br>In fact my last duel was a 49 Monk VS my 47 pally.  The monk ran for thier life at 15% health... stating damn that wurmy hurts. I did not have to use lay hands and was chasing the monk with well over 60%mana left.<br><br>Stick with it brothers and sisters.. you will find that we can solo where others group.  We survive where others die.  We are the ones to save group members when the cleric fails.  We are ordained by the hands of the Gods.  Do not let jealous mortals sway your emotions..<br><br>Battle on and be victorious<br>&nbsp;<br>Sartoran Battleskar<br>52nd Cavalier of Brell<br>The Tribunal---&gt; Vis Veres</td></tr>
