	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, I can't commet on my elven brethren, however I've livedthe Paladin life quite well as a Human.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's a nicely rounded race, not too weak, not too dumb, not too slow.  Basically it makes you an average Paladin for the begining of your life, tho, after 40 or so, you really begin to excell in groups and on your own...make friends, save some chaps life with LoH while wanderig around sometime...they'll help later.<br>&nbsp;<br>Armadausll Marrutin<br>50th Paladin of Saryrn<br>Proud member of Celtica.<br>(Yes those are L's in my name)</td></tr>
