	   <tr><td colspan=2>Kay.<br><br>Either one may start in Qeynos, however, he must worship Karana or Rodcet Nife.&nbsp;&nbsp;Human is the most well-rounded and half elves have low wis and I *think* slightly lower str than humans.  (However, I say elves, even half-elves, are curvier than humans.  *laugh*)  However, vision is always a plus.  You'll need to sink points into wisdom during character creation as a Half-Elf, and you should probably go 15-5 strength and wisdom as a human.  This is only my opinion, however.  I went 10-5-5 str wis cha and I get along fine.<br><br>I started in Freeport and I got along just fine, especially with the dock to Faydwer nearby.  *shrug*  It all depends on what you wanna do.  Blackburrow and Butcherblock are both excellent hunting grounds for low level people.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dalantia Dragonfury<br>Crusader of the Burning Heart, 60th Protection, Third Blessing<br>Fennin Ro<br>New Dawnings<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60479" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60479</a></td></tr>
